    <a href="https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/pidgin">libpurple0</a>
    <span>
        <a href="https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/pidgin/1:2.7.11-1ubuntu2.2">1:2.7.11-1ubuntu2.2</a>
    </span>
  </dd>
    
  

<dt>Ubuntu 10.04 LTS:</dt>
  
    
  <dd>
    <a href="https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/pidgin">finch</a>
    <span>
        <a href="https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/pidgin/1:2.6.6-1ubuntu4.5">1:2.6.6-1ubuntu4.5</a>
    </span>
  </dd>
    
  
    
  <dd>
    <a href="https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/pidgin">pidgin</a>
    <span>
        <a href="https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/pidgin/1:2.6.6-1ubuntu4.5">1:2.6.6-1ubuntu4.5</a>
    </span>
  </dd>
    
  
    
  <dd>
    <a href="https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/pidgin">libpurple0</a>
    <span>
        <a href="https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/pidgin/1:2.6.6-1ubuntu4.5">1:2.6.6-1ubuntu4.5</a>
    </span>
  </dd>
    
  

</dl>
<p>To update your system, please follow these instructions:
<a href="https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Security/Upgrades">https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Security/Upgrades</a>.
</p>
<p>After a standard system update you need to restart Pidgin to make<br />all the necessary changes.<br /></p>



